Definition: believing the worst of human nature and motives
Example: having a sneering disbelief in e.g. selflessness of others
Synonyms: noun, person, cynic, misanthropic, attribute, misanthropy, misanthropical, misanthrope, believing, the, worst, of, human, nature, and, motives, having, a, sneering, disbelief, in, e, g, selflessness, others
Category: adj.all
